PrecisOrder prescribing an additional period of one year during which certain TRAVEL AND ACCOMMODATION EXPENSES may be reimbursed to the Hon. Mr. Justice R. DENNIS MAHER, a Judge of Her Majesty's Court of Queen's Bench for Saskatchewan, who was required to relocate from the City of North Battleford to the City of Prince Albert.
